    microsoft/CryptoNets CryptoNets 演示了在使用同態加密加密的數據上使用神經網路。同態加密允許在數據加密時對數據執行加法和乘法等操作。因此，它允許在外包計算時保持數據的私密性（有關同態加密及其應用的更多資訊，請參閱此處和此處）。該專案演示了使用同態加密進行外包神經網路預測。考慮到的場景是一個供應商，該提供者希望提供預測即服務 （PaaS），但需要預測的數據可能是私有的。在衛生或金融等領域可能是這種情況。通過使用CryptoNets，該服務的使用者可以使用同態加密來加密其數據，並僅將加密的消息發送給服務提供者。由於同態加密允許提供者在數據加密時對數據進行操作，因此提供者可以使用預先訓練的神經網路進行預測，同時數據在整個過程中保持加密狀態，並最終將預測發送給可以解密結果的使用者。在此過程中，服務提供者不會瞭解有關所使用的數據、所做的預測或任何中間結果的任何資訊，因為在整個過程中，所有內容都是加密的。此專案使用 Microsoft Research 開發的同態加密的簡單加密算術庫 SEAL 版本 3.2.1 實現。 100

    microsoft/hash-and-cache Allows you to wrap caching behavior around an arbitrary command. It will take in a list of source files, generate a hash, then check a cache (stored in Azure Storage) to see if those inputs have been seen before. If so it will download the cached outputs instead of running the command. If no cache is found matching the hash it will run the command instead. 1

    microsoft/EconML ALICE (Automated Learning and Intelligence for Causation and Economics) is a Microsoft Research project aimed at applying Artificial Intelligence concepts to economic decision making. One of its goals is to build a toolkit that combines state-of-the-art machine learning techniques with econometrics in order to bring automation to complex causal inference problems. To date, the ALICE Python SDK (econml) implements orthogonal machine learning algorithms such as the double machine learning work of Chernozhukov et al. This toolkit is designed to measure the causal effect of some treatment variable(s) t on an outcome variable y, controlling for a set of features x. 698

    microsoft/MSMARCO-對話搜索 真正的對話式搜索是生成智慧且有用的 AI 的旅程中的下一個邏輯步驟。為了理解這可能意味著什麼，研究人員一直希望研究人們目前如何與搜尋引擎交談。傳統上，製作如此全面的數據集的願望受到限制，因為擁有這些數據的人（搜尋引擎）對用戶負有維護其隱私的責任，並且不能以維護使用者對搜尋引擎的信任的方式公開共享數據。鑒於這兩股強大的力量，我們相信我們擁有滿足這兩組需求的數據集和範式：一個近似真實數據的人工公共數據集，以及評估模型對真實用戶行為性能的能力。這意味著我們發佈了一個公共數據集，該數據集是通過使用嵌入相似性創建人工會話來生成的，並將在原始數據上進行測試。再說一遍：我們沒有發佈任何私人用戶數據，但發佈了我們認為可以很好地代表真實使用者交互的數據。 56
    microsoft/AzureMonitorAddonForSplunk 一個 Splunk 外掛程式（又名模組化輸入），可將來自各種 Azure ARM 資源的指標和診斷日誌以及訂閱範圍的活動日誌（也稱為審核日誌）引入 Splunk Enterprise。 53

    微軟/OpenKP 自動提取與文檔含義相關的關鍵短語是語義文檔理解的重要步驟。有效的關鍵詞提取 （KPE） 系統可以使廣泛的自然語言處理和資訊檢索任務受益。最近的神經方法將該任務表述為文檔到關鍵短語、序列到序列的任務。與以前的 KPE 系統相比，這些 seq2seq 學習模型顯示出有希望的結果 神經 KPE 的最新進展主要在源自科學領域的檔中觀察到。在實際場景中，KPE 的大多數潛在應用程式都處理源自稀疏來源的各種文檔。這些檔不太可能包括結構、散文，並且寫得像科學論文一樣好。它們通常包含多種多樣的文檔結構，並存在於不同的領域中，其內容針對的受眾比科學家更廣泛。為了鼓勵研究界開發一個強大的神經模型，在開放領域中提取關鍵短語，我們創建了OpenKP：一個包含超過150,000個文檔的數據集，其中最相關的關鍵詞是由專家註釋生成的。 46

    microsoft/ts-parsec Writing a custom parser is a fairly common need. Although there are already parser combinators in others languages, TypeScript provides a powerful and well-structured foundation for building this. Common parser combinators’ weakness are error handling and ambiguity resolving, but these are ts-parsec’s important features. Additionally, ts-parsec provides a very easy to use programming interface, that could help people to build programming-language-scale parsers in just a few hours. This technology has already been used in Microsoft/react-native-tscodegen. 17

    microsoft/SecCon-Framework Security configuration is complex. With thousands of group policies available in Windows, choosing the “best” setting is difficult. It’s not always obvious which permutations of policies are required to implement a complete scenario, and there are often unintended consequences of some security lockdowns. The SECCON Baselines divide configuration into Productivity Devices and Privileged Access Workstations. This document will focus on Productivity Devices (SECCON 5, 4, and 3). Microsoft’s current guidance on Privileged Access Workstations can be found at http://aka.ms/cyberpaw and as part of the Securing Privileged Access roadmap found at http://aka.ms/privsec. 52

    microsoft/Build-Mobile-App-with-Chat The tutorial uses several Azure services to power a real-time chat infrastructure that is readymade for analytics. Event Hubs ingest chat messages received from websites running in Web Apps. Web Jobs are used to pull chat messages from Event Hubs, invoke the Text Analytics API to apply sentiment scores to each message and to forward messages to Service Bus Topics from which chat participants receive their messages. Stream Analytics is used to drive the archival of scored chat messages into Document DB and Azure Search is used to make the stored chat messages full text searchable. 22

    microsoft/SaaSApp-ContosoShopkeeper The focus of this quick start is on leveraging Elastic Pools and understanding how the support the backend for a SaaS application like Contoso ShopKeeper, the design and implementation of the App Services component is considered out of scope. Since the best way to understand the behavior of Elastic Pools is to experience using them under load, we provide a load generator. The load generator is a console application that targets one or more elastic database instances in an Elastic Pool with a specific write load. You can run multiple instances of the load generator with different settings if you want to create a blended load, e.g., a mix of heavy a light load. In addition, you do not need to target all databases in the pool by the load generator, so you can leave databases you choose without any load. 9
